        "body": "# Hi\n\n## I would like to contribute by translating the entire 30 Days of Python repository into French. My plan is to:\n\n- Create a directory structure for French contents (which one `/fr` or `/French`)\n- Translate the markdown files for each day\n- If applicable, also provide translated versions of code comments and documentation\n- Should I commit the translation once I finish all files or as I complete each file?\n\nThis will help reach more learners, especially French-speaking beginners.\n\nI am ready to get started once I have your feedback!\n\nThanks!",
