        "body": "Hi Momokh,\r\n\r\nThank you for your email. Thank you for your contribution and if there\u2019s no\r\nany exiting French, you can translate it.\r\n\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nAsabeneh\r\n\r\nOn Sun, May 17, 2026, 2:00\u202fPM Momokh99 ***@***.***> wrote:\r\n\r\n> *Momokh99* created an issue (Asabeneh/30-Days-Of-Python#837)\r\n> <https://github.com/Asabeneh/30-Days-Of-Python/issues/837>\r\n> Hi\r\n>\r\n> ##I would like to contribute by translating the entire 30 Days of Python\r\n> repository into French. My plan is to:\r\n>\r\n>    - Create a directory structure for French contents (which one /fr or\r\n>    /French)\r\n>    - Translate the markdown files for each day\r\n>    - If applicable, also provide translated versions of code comments and\r\n>    documentation\r\n>    - Should I commit the translation once I finish all files or as I\r\n>    complete each file?\r\n>\r\n> This will help reach more learners, especially French-speaking beginners.\r\n>\r\n> I am ready to get started once I have your feedback!\r\n>\r\n> Thanks!\r\n>\r\n> \u2014\r\n> Reply to this email directly, view it on GitHub\r\n> <https://github.com/Asabeneh/30-Days-Of-Python/issues/837>, or unsubscribe\r\n> <https://github.com/notifications/unsubscribe-auth/ACEXHPZN6BVVOSANKGK3H4T43GLTLAVCNFSM6AAAAACZBJVC6KVHI2DSMVQWIX3LMV43ASLTON2WKOZUGQ3DGMRTHEZTMOA>\r\n> .\r\n> Triage notifications on the go with GitHub Mobile for iOS\r\n> <https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1477376905?ct=notification-email&mt=8&pt=524675>\r\n> or Android\r\n> <https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.github.android&referrer=utm_campaign%3Dnotification-email%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Dgithub>.\r\n>\r\n> You are receiving this because you are subscribed to this thread.Message\r\n> ID: ***@***.***>\r\n>\r\n",
